### Get Investment Summary
GET https://localhost:7192/api/v1/investments
Accept: application/json

###

### Get All Transactions
GET https://localhost:7192/api/v1/investments/transactions
Accept: application/json

###

### Create New Transaction - Nvidia
POST https://localhost:7192/api/v1/investments/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assetSymbol": "NVDA",
  "assetName": "Nvidia",
  "assetType": 0,
  "type": 0,
  "date": "2024-01-15T00:00:00Z",
  "amount": 25.00,
  "sharesQuantity": 0.271237,
  "sharePrice": 92.48,
  "fees": 1.00,
  "notes": "Test transaction from Excel data"
}

###

### Create New Transaction - Apple
POST https://localhost:7192/api/v1/investments/transactions
