###

### Get Transactions by Asset
GET https://localhost:7192/api/v1/investments/transactions?assetSymbol=NVDA
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Current Holdings
GET https://localhost:7192/api/v1/investments/holdings
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Specific Asset Holding
GET https://localhost:7192/api/v1/investments/holdings/NVDA
Accept: application/json

###

### Get All Assets
GET https://localhost:7192/api/v1/investments/assets
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Transactions by Date Range
GET https://localhost:7192/api/v1/investments/transactions?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Accept: application/json

###

### Update Transaction (replace {id} with actual transaction ID)
PUT https://localhost:7192/api/v1/investments/transactions/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assetSymbol": "NVDA",
  "assetName": "Nvidia",
  "assetType": 0,
  "type": 0,
  "date": "2024-01-15T00:00:00Z",
  "amount": 30.00,
  "sharesQuantity": 0.271237,
  "sharePrice": 92.48,
  "fees": 1.00,
  "notes": "Updated transaction"
}

###

### Delete Transaction (replace {id} with actual transaction ID)
DELETE https://localhost:7192/api/v1/investments/transactions/{id}
